Shipper took a very long time to send. Most every other shipper on this platform changes the status to Packed only when they’re actually going to send. They changed to packed the same day as order placed. Then they waited 6 days before moving to courier to ship from overseas. Luckily, the process from arriving to China facility to Vietnam facility went pretty quickly. The image online definitely looks like a nice material than received, but it was a gamble to order and see the quality first hand. Worth the price paid? Yes. Would order again? Probably not.
